{"tid":2117380,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"官方宣佈2020金球獎取消 首次中斷","createTime":"2020-07-20T21:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T12:38:03.000Z","uid":173952,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"1516ff95f1f60baab774a796fe6f12d5786e674e","tid":2117380,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T21:35:48.000Z","msg":"香港時間7月20日，《法國足球》官方宣佈2020金球獎取消，因為由於缺乏足夠公平的評選條件。<br />\n<br />\n  《法國足球》在聲明中表示，2020年是一個特殊的年份，由於各聯賽情況不同，有的提前結束，有的中斷後復賽，無法保證所有球員在一個公平的體系下進行評選，因此最好的辦法是取消今年的金球獎評選。自從1956年金球獎創立以來，這是第一次出現取消評獎的情況。<br />\n<br />\n  金球獎是由法國《隊報》旗下雜誌《法國足球》自1956年起舉辦的授予每年度最優秀的歐洲足球運動員的獎項，也是世界球壇上最負盛名、影響力最大的足球獎項評選之一。"},{"pid":"adb8346c17651fe59ffb8ce82cd5146def0d0927","tid":2117380,"uid":173952,"like":45,"dislike":24,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T21:36:43.000Z","msg":"巴塞一輸左西甲，就宣佈取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d200ce1fde65c5b141e209ab2f3bcf846f4108c","tid":2117380,"uid":173952,"like":8,"dislike":13,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T21:37:57.000Z","msg":"利雲表示:dllm"},{"pid":"fdcf725d7de33dd715b784629142c39c0dbf23a7","tid":2117380,"uid":18279,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T22:15:48.000Z","msg":"法甲取消所以不公平？"},{"pid":"6ba8ce19b9f4634302b80884050f6043e70ee2f6","tid":2117380,"uid":173952,"like":15,"dislike":16,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fdcf725d7de33dd715b784629142c39c0dbf23a7","tid":2117380,"uid":18279,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T22:15:48.000Z","msg":"法甲取消所以不公平？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T23:53:18.000Z","msg":"巴塞無冠軍，唔公平"},{"pid":"e59fbebfe2948444532f4be81aeaaf738323cf56","tid":2117380,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T23:59:59.000Z","msg":"美斯獎"},{"pid":"a80ad2bb4650cb75150afaa93c5251062c7aee7e","tid":2117380,"uid":25345,"like":17,"dislike":6,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T00:05:54.000Z","msg":"梅西冇冠軍<br />\n取消"},{"pid":"b76